{"tid":1625333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［分化撚］屌曬你地全部人老母","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:53:52.000Z","uid":141784,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa5382c819308f1e61b5431622ff48debc82d696","tid":1625333,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:36:38.000Z","msg":"對唔住 唔係想分化<br />\n但係到左呢個moment 真係唔屌唔得<br />\n一望到連登今日就係不斷 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己人打自己人</span></strong><br />\n不斷有人係到帶風向 今日出去係反對蒙面法 本來我係贊成<br />\n琴日18區快閃係有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成果</span></span></strong> <br />\n但係同樣都為我地帶黎左一場<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">與論戰</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請各位記住一點！ <br />\n香港示威者<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係暴徒</span></span></strong><br />\n我地只係搞啲<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抹黑示威者既鋪頭</span></span></strong> 呢一樣係一定要澄清<br />\n<br />\n依伽打開電視就會見到 CCTVB日日係到講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">示威者點破壞 </span></strong></span>完全<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">無講過點解</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後 點解前線會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">灰心</span></span>點解有一日會無人肯出黎 請你地記住 因為你地班仆街真係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">當前線係condom</span></span></strong>啊 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">新屋嶺有料煲 見記者會話停用就無再講過<br />\n失禁同中槍個兩位手足有無人跟啊？<br />\n琴日14歲個個中學生呢？</span></span></strong>你問下有無廢老知琴晚有無個咁細既學生中槍啊？<br />\n<br />\n我地係要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">耗盡警方</span></span> <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔係要令示威者無曬精力</span></span></strong><br />\n有幾多黑材料都無用啦 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班仆街都唔撚post唔撚推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">11月區議會選舉啊 咪再覺得同淺黃/淺藍溝通無用啊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我係柒婆一定好開心 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔洗熄連登 就可以搞到連登分化</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n依伽最緊要係與論 解釋 唔係出去送頭<br />\n求下你地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔好睇小與論</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fc10d09011d8ec2dde060b0b98b3eae897603f27","tid":1625333,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"e923224e18cd18d3e1ccba2fe9de031d373a63b4","tid":1625333,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"e4b9c615bc92dc726458b3f9482441e6aed139f4","tid":1625333,"uid":321913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"［裝修指南］維港沿岸篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624936</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f7bd9b366e2bba6757f8ce788f9a55e0a0c7825","tid":1625333,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"33725f7a3682b16a584409e8cd58665d2759eafe","tid":1625333,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"ff415d37e772ec5b9c7df4fc1550d532f7aae895","tid":1625333,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"18b7fe4adacedbec7d3121e7dd318aef577e7e6b","tid":1625333,"uid":141784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"7995f25a02a7ddd6258723145281b01aebb444a6","tid":1625333,"uid":122217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"到今時今日仲做標題撚<br />\n好心收皮啦<b